About Phgstats 0.6.2:
-------------------

Functions of Phgstats 0.6.2:
--------------------------

Phgstats is a gameserver status script that gets data from the server and shows
it sorted as html-code so that players and clans can watch on their 
website what goes on at their server. It can display one ore more servers.

The following games and modification are supported at the moment:

     Game:                           Gamename Variable:
    - American's Army               aa
    - Armagetronad                  atron
